name: Biplane Duel
description:
Biplane Duel is a homage to the Intellivision Biplanes game included in Triple Action.

Two players are pitted against each other in WWI era biplanes, dogfighting for supremacy in the air. Avoid the ground and obstacles, while weaving through the air, avoid stalling or use it to your advantage on your opponent. The first one to fifteen victories is the winner.
